{"tid":955561,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［語言學習］求香港法文地方推介","createTime":"2018-12-25T13:40:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T07:19:20.000Z","uid":7678,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ba7bfc1ba81346dbcb2904e49777f7d9dd92f17d","tid":955561,"uid":7678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T13:40:57.000Z","msg":"小弟之前係法國文化協會學左岩岩好2年<br />\n程度介乎A2 - B1 左右，但停左一年。<br />\n<br />\n而家想學返，但法國文化協會又轉哂制，又要屈我留班兼買過哂新教材，開班時間又唔岩（小弟星期一至五朝九晚六返工，而且都要OT)<br />\n<br />\n但發現香港好少地方有提供方便在職人士/成人既法文course, 就算有都係A101 introduction 級別<br />\n<br />\n跪求推介！！"},{"pid":"2978e0eb3ba7c61a1dd685692b4d8675a8b71251","tid":955561,"uid":115888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T14:06:47.000Z","msg":"同求 私補都照殺"},{"pid":"a42bb6c9fa8222eecb80990747d7f0f20d86095b","tid":955561,"uid":7678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T16:29:14.000Z","msg":"私補都得"},{"pid":"f849d8d2a7ba3330dbdd7514a822ad42099f4732","tid":955561,"uid":138557,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T16:34:26.000Z","msg":"點解想學"},{"pid":"dd65a9066c01e1aa6616fbdde225484e57c2faeb","tid":955561,"uid":7678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f849d8d2a7ba3330dbdd7514a822ad42099f4732","tid":955561,"uid":138557,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T16:34:26.000Z","msg":"點解想學"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T16:39:12.000Z","msg":"興趣"},{"pid":"392ab1ed367713d5528caaea93a2dc6f9937de0b","tid":955561,"uid":138557,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"dd65a9066c01e1aa6616fbdde225484e57c2faeb","tid":955561,"uid":7678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f849d8d2a7ba3330dbdd7514a822ad42099f4732","tid":955561,"uid":138557,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T16:34:26.000Z","msg":"點解想學"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T16:39:12.000Z","msg":"興趣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T16:46:20.000Z","msg":"個答案萬能架啵<img src=\"/asse